# Project rules

Follow `AGENTS.md` as the source of truth for this repository.

- Use Bun by default.
- Keep the app Cloudflare Workers compatible.
- Do not run development server or database migration commands unless the user explicitly asks in the same turn.
- Prefer the existing TanStack Start, Tailwind, Radix/shadcn-style, Drizzle, Better Auth, and Cloudflare direction.
- Do not use pnpm or npm unless the user explicitly asks.
